Title: Friends in Low Places
Description:
When we crashed, the nerubians were upon us in an instant. We would have lost nearly everyone we brought with us, had someone not intervened.

I do not know who--or what--stepped in on our behalf. But if there is even a shred of hope that we have allies in this place then we must seize upon it and refuse to let go.
ObjectivesText: Search the Breathing Pit for your mysterious protector.
RewardText: Ah! You survived. Excellent. You have much to do.
